Parents in Gauteng have until midnight tonight to submit online applications to secure space for their children in Grade 1 and Grade 8 for the 2019 academic year.
Applications through the online admissions system opened on April 16 and will close at midnight.
From 18 July, the department will inform parents in which school their child has been placed.
Gauteng education member for the executive council (MEC) Panyaza Lesufi said the deadline will not be extended.
– African News Agency (ANA)
